Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.07,0:46:43.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}「あたし行かなくちゃ」
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.55,0:46:50.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時は止まるはずもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.97,0:46:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}願いは風に消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.41,0:47:02.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}喉は乾いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.07,0:47:06.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}この先には何があるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:09.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}二人は平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.54,0:47:12.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向かない君は強い
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.01,0:47:15.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}もう交わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.12,0:47:19.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}立ちつくす街は歪み
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.28,0:47:22.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君が居た記憶だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.52,0:47:25.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}胸の中に溢れ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.91,0:47:32.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}深い海を創り　僕はそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.23,0:47:35.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}溺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.63,0:48:31.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憂鬱な目覚め　隠せない絶望
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.88,0:48:37.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それでも世界は美しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.76,0:48:40.96,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It made me sad
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.30,0:48:50.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I want to see you, remember again...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.05,0:48:54.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}握り締めた冷たい指
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.31,0:48:57.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は悲しく笑い
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.29,0:49:00.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}僕はかける言葉もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.78,0:49:03.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}景色は滲む
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.04,0:49:06.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}始まればいずれ終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:10.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}綺麗事などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.43,0:49:13.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}せめて君を温めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.82,0:49:24.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ほんの少しの時間を与えて　神様
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.63,0:49:33.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}眩しすぎる朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.91,0:49:39.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}諦め誘うんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.42,0:49:46.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}全てさらけ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.93,0:49:54.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}この身を委ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.07,0:46:43.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须前去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.55,0:46:50.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}时间不会停留
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.97,0:46:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}心愿被风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.41,0:47:02.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}喉咙干涩沙哑
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.07,0:47:06.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知前方有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:09.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你我就像一组平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.54,0:47:12.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坚强的你从不回头
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.01,0:47:15.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们将永远不再相交
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.12,0:47:19.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我颓然而立 城市在视野中模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.28,0:47:22.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有你曾存在的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.52,0:47:25.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}冲垮心灵的堤坝
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.91,0:47:32.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}流淌成一片深海 将我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.23,0:47:35.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}深深淹没
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.63,0:48:31.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在忧郁中醒来 难掩心中绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.88,0:48:37.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}然而世界依旧美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.76,0:48:40.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令我悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.30,0:48:50.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要见到你 再度忆起...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.05,0:48:54.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握紧冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.31,0:48:57.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}脸上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.29,0:49:00.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.78,0:49:03.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有视野渐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.04,0:49:06.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言语粉饰
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:10.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}有始必定有终
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.43,0:49:13.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}唯愿能将你温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.82,0:49:24.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}神啊 请给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.63,0:49:33.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}晨曦的光芒太过耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.91,0:49:39.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.42,0:49:46.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.93,0:49:54.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任凭此身沉浮
