Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如往常的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如往常的上学路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那一天的警报改变了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛已不再是平常的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经置身于战斗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,02
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 真的大家都要做驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前是代码形成值最高的六个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会和你一样接受训练 准备应对实战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…大家的爸爸妈妈都没有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,候补驾驶员的意愿都已经确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而对大人们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们出生之前 他们就知道总有一天会迎来这种局面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经不需要过问他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…我一个人不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不也只靠我们俩就解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又不是敌人的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你以为我能把整个岛都托付给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 大家都是稀里糊涂就当上驾驶员的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们马上就会清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练就是为此而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就快到了 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要做些准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我要先问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 你怎么没穿Alvis的制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西 我就是不想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为穿上就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要活在与之前截然不同的常识中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 穿上制服是接受的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 你要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想活下去 这是最必不可少的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…从很早之前就知道了吧 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但并不是全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是今后的事 还有很多是未知数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 春日井 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 春日井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 早啊 羽佐间 今天看起来挺精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 难得感觉挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 不过 别太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井 你一个人在等啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看Alvis的内部 就早来了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这里实在太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要接受有这种地方存在的事实就够不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 春日井同学 你怎么没穿Alvis的制服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿是不是不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑你也没穿制服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋你没收到制服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 就是…不想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见和羽佐间你们不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？就是件衣服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得是在逼我去做另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间你没想法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我有种很特别的感觉 我还挺喜欢这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 怎么回事 我们居然是最晚到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么都起得那么早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剑司你起得太晚了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…话说你们那身是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良你们也不想穿制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非得穿那个不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸我妈都没说什么耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我穿那种不方便活动的东西 我才不干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 还好不是我一个人没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 早上好 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 甲洋 咲良 剑司 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的制服呢 应该都发到手上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要穿那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校都没有校服的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们马上去借备用的制服换上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那什么语气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方需要你们优先遵守纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我自作主张！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凭自己的意志到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没资格命令我穿制服！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱指挥的人只有当场排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士你个混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头 等等别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们不好 别生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么态度啊！气死我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了 咲良 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是你的衣柜 得好好珍惜才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意要怎么穿嘛 真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士原来是那种发号施令的人吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是本来就觉得他挺冷漠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也用不着那么生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容不得开玩笑这点和岛上的大人一个样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然听大人说这是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就乖乖地信了的我们倒也挺那啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被叫去开机器人消灭敌人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说都是会笑掉大牙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最可能会笑的大人却都一脸严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着心里都要发毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能开机器人 其他的都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会是什么样的机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你神经真是大条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…真的是我们的岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得穿上这身制服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所知道的岛就已经消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在不知不觉间来到了陌生的地方一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是大人擅自在岛上建了秘密基地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么厉害的秘密基地 亏他们造得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想早点开上机器人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服了你们 跟你们在一起都紧张不起来啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,03
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟室 听得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始进行瞑想训练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员进入模拟驾驶座 体验精神视野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神…视野？那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢 你听得懂在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…感觉上明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你用我们都听得懂的话来说 总士老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是体验你们自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们将会看到一片海 那是你们的心具体化的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是虚拟现实中的海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你们能在其中自由活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算通过了第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 机器人呢 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在海里玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点教我们怎么去用干掉敌人的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是适应性测试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每个人的心将会决定你们该驾驶哪一部法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 甲洋 剑司 卫 进入驾驶座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用连接线缆 把手伸进尼伯龙根的指环就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指环…是指这个装在座位上的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…不会坐上去就下不来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 卫 你进去看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你自己进去不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 亏我还那么期待 以为可以开机器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像游乐园 虽然其实没去过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干这种事有个鸟用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候到了这么大的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…海底？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是虚拟现实的海？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮得刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…怎么回事 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冰？上面全都被冰盖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 我的心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 为什么会这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的海 常夏的海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…话说 为什么我能站在海上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是珊瑚礁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 又漂亮又暖和 我这人真是和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 爽死了爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害 我在乘风破浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又有个大浪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好厉害啊 太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好带劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有的 深深的海底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人…也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在连光也到达不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然感到非常平静
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,04
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学他们是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点动静也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 你不用休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要坐一会儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 我没事 今天状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不舒服了就马上说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你去跟皆城说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她都说没事了 你就别理她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子也是自愿来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摆什么监护人的架子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆 摆监护人的架子…你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子你也是的 被人这么黏着你就不嫌烦的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都不知道 为什么要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你就不爽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把翔子当小公主似的哄着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是这样能让你好像很了不起所以心里痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么资格这么说我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你们都别吵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟室 不许窃窃私语！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在说你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们四个 先出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的三个 进驾驶座去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体上还留着寒意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那又暖和又漂亮 简直棒呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想再去一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？卫 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里面的时候的事我都模模糊糊的 不怎么想得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要跟总士说一声 叫他让你休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 我可不想一个人因为这种事被除外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且剑司和咲良都在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想当驾驶员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良说要当 剑司也说要当 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是自己决定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是脑子有点短路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是平时就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司 别拖卫下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想当驾驶员的话 自己一个人去当就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要牵连朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫牵连啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自说自话什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自说自话的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他陪你做这种危险的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做你就一个人去做！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么蠢话 你个混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么突然打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我安静点！现在还在训练！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司！你为什么想当什么驾驶员！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关你屁事！混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！叫你住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,05
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服的风…好漂亮的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面有海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…飞在天上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 一眼看去全是海水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到很远 很远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然能像这样自由地飞在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却突然什么都感觉不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围都是雾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚下却像镜子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海？原来这里是海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯独我在的地方没有波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平静的水上 只有我在走动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既碰不到海 也进不了海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围只有雾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是怎么回事 到处都乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会溺水的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 海…好热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越热了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨？连雨都是烫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 给我停下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会淹死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下！救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:09.53,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,665)}Blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 咲良！振作一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你别勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别硬要站起来啊 先坐一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 甲洋 剑司 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入驾驶座 继续训练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下 咲良都撑不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们丢下她不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会替她做检查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点症状很快就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点？这样绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续训练 别以为你们还有空担心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 别管我 快点进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司 让她一个人静一静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 你可别逞强啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,06
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 感觉好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司 你为什么不下海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么…有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里又安全又和平还舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果5秒之内你不下海 我就采取强制措施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！我绝对不干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会离开安全的地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 难得那么漂亮的珊瑚礁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手！别破坏我的地盘啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 海突然变暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么原地不动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么冷的海里 我不想动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冷得都快晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我兴奋起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这浪太高了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 可以飞得好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高 好高 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.62,0:23:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本看不见海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼 这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光线好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候…我在往下掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透明的水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一碰到就觉得…好像对面还有一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:24:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要弄不清到底哪一个才是真正的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像我被关在对面一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在抓着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 放开我 不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深深的海底
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深 好深 好深 深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.98,0:25:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.72,0:25:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我…一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.00,0:25:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是…一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.55,0:25:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 黑暗的海…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体要被压扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.27,0:25:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.36,0:25:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.13,0:25:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太重…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.96,0:25:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.64,0:25:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.89,0:26:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑到规定时间的还是只有一骑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是意料之中的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.33,0:26:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是居然要用齐格飞系统整合这么支离破碎的印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.32,0:26:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.97,0:26:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让所有人都能在战斗中活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.01,0:26:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,07
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.94,0:26:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.21,0:26:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来还是所有人都被搞晕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.15,0:26:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个绝对是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.17,0:26:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉脑子一片空白 根本想不起出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.28,0:26:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练的内容居然是要被人摆弄自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.85,0:27:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 你没事吧？不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.81,0:27:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 今天我也有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.21,0:27:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.34,0:27:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都碰上那种事了还这么有精神 没想到你挺坚强的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.73,0:27:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.92,0:27:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为某人保护过度 才让她显得好像很弱而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.52,0:27:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 我还没说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.93,0:27:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装得好像很强的样子 结果第一个出局的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫出局 你个混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.82,0:27:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.30,0:27:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你们在吵什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.73,0:27:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.28,0:27:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 都是朋友 何必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 你们不觉得有人在听我们的对话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.15,0:27:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人…是谁？为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.60,0:27:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.84,0:27:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在这里被测试
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前有人倒下也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.31,0:27:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就像是某种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.96,0:27:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是被当成了实验的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.04,0:28:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.08,0:28:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.87,0:28:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过测试就行了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋 你挺多疑的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.69,0:28:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扯这些了 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.14,0:28:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.46,0:28:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…就算了 总觉得不想吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.78,0:28:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.03,0:28:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠哉游哉的话 感觉总士又会来下命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.25,0:28:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.82,0:28:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.20,0:28:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫 你真的没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.13,0:28:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只是有点茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.11,0:28:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的成了驾驶员 就会一直碰到危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.18,0:28:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你却被剑司给拉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.10,0:29:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会觉得不情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.47,0:29:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在勉强的不是我 而是剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.74,0:29:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司其实很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.12,0:29:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为有咲良 所以才强作坚强的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.60,0:29:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为咲良？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.88,0:29:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有哭 尽管失去了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.87,0:29:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司他很明白失去爸爸的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想待在咲良身边
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.96,0:29:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.76,0:29:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要自己去冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.12,0:29:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的有危险 那更得在一起才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.89,0:29:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为彼此是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.93,0:29:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起…？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.39,0:29:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能什么也帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是陪在身边是能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.41,0:29:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑你应该也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.08,0:29:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.06,0:29:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是因为想陪在总士身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.51,0:29:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.43,0:29:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.01,0:29:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.75,0:29:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我想…应该是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.98,0:30:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 你又来找茬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.79,0:30:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.04,0:30:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.06,0:30:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你干嘛啊 突然道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.61,0:30:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没啥啦…你明白了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 翔子 你真的没勉强自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.49,0:30:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有句话可能不应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.44,0:30:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我特别开心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.31,0:30:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.49,0:30:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够像这样和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.46,0:30:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.11,0:30:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的让我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.99,0:30:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.83,0:30:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.71,0:30:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.56,0:30:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 唯独这件事我就是想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.57,0:30:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想试一试 能做到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.97,0:31:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,08
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.72,0:31:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人 都进入精神视野了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.29,0:31:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我会整合你们所有人的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.63,0:31:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴就在视野的某个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.78,0:31:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要找出彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.59,0:31:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴 这种空空荡荡 冷冰冰的海里会有什么同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.16,0:31:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会其实同伴根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.20,0:31:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就就只有我一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.71,0:31:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会其实大家都在之前的战斗里死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.38,0:31:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 有可能其实岛早就没有了 只剩下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.38,0:31:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 冰海
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.83,0:31:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.56,0:31:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.96,0:32:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.92,0:32:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 真是个漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.48,0:32:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.94,0:32:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的海直到刚才都还一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.49,0:32:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然看到了光 于是就追了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.45,0:32:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒意渐渐消退了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.49,0:32:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.53,0:32:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才还像要被冻住一样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一来 就有一点点…不那么冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.58,0:32:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也没有 什么地方也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.94,0:32:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个映在镜面一样的海面上的我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.60,0:33:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是平的 涌不起一丁点感情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 对面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.53,0:33:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是我自以为在担心翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实早就被她嫌烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.25,0:33:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 对面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.52,0:33:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前 我对翔子做了很糟糕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.99,0:33:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 小时候带着翔子上山去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.72,0:33:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为翔子一直待在房间里 说她很想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.05,0:34:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始她还很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.25,0:34:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在山上就突然变得脸色铁青
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.06,0:34:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体越来越冷 动也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.44,0:34:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边又没有一个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.63,0:34:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.49,0:34:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差一点就把翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.50,0:34:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是只是在把自责的心情强加给翔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.18,0:34:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 对面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.91,0:34:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.72,0:34:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:35:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围都只有雾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.96,0:35:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.04,0:35:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有风…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.97,0:35:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾 渐渐散了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.72,0:35:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.29,0:35:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从天上…为什么 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.29,0:35:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.67,0:35:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.99,0:35:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 翔子…哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.62,0:35:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在飞 我在飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.30,0:35:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.92,0:35:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你以前带我走一样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.67,0:35:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.54,0:35:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.62,0:35:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的海
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这么高的地方 你是怎么找到我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.60,0:35:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.36,0:35:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.50,0:36:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分明就只看得到自己
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.32,0:36:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 真矢 我们去一骑同学那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.11,0:36:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你想去就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.17,0:36:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来决定要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.83,0:36:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方 我相信我的行动可以比任何人都更自由
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.83,0:36:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真和平 我绝对不会离开这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事情我都不会走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.09,0:36:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.93,0:36:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴要来了 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.79,0:36:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧跑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.66,0:37:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边有个大浪要打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.06,0:37:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 一开始虽然吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.98,0:37:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在我已经适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.65,0:37:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.84,0:37:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海好烫 更烫点 再烫点吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.00,0:37:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更乱七八糟一点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.53,0:37:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加 更加 更加！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.95,0:37:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉兴奋起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.08,0:37:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.79,0:37:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会输呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.07,0:37:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的珊瑚礁…我的和平之地要被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.16,0:37:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.87,0:37:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹…闹得更大点！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.55,0:37:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,09
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 冰被砸碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.53,0:38:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.36,0:38:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.50,0:38:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑黑的乌云飘过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.54,0:38:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.06,0:38:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 一骑同学在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.57,0:38:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学他…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.79,0:38:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.54,0:38:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.11,0:38:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.73,0:38:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要掉下去了 翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.63,0:38:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面 有冰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.85,0:38:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 快飞起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.98,0:38:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会掉到冰上的！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.11,0:38:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！妈妈救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.53,0:39:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲 甲洋 把冰消掉 她们要掉下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.93,0:39:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 这个地方是我的 我不想要它被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变得这么厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.00,0:39:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好冷 怎么会这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.75,0:39:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.99,0:39:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 害怕别人骗我 害怕别人背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.66,0:39:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 不要靠近我！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.46,0:39:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋 我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.98,0:39:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.93,0:39:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 低下头！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.09,0:39:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我怀里来！快点
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.66,0:39:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 波浪…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.41,0:39:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冷突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.65,0:39:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷电正在击碎冰块
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.15,0:39:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.24,0:39:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更强点 更强点 更强点！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.23,0:40:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会输呢！上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.50,0:40:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.24,0:40:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.86,0:40:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰被打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.18,0:40:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.92,0:40:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.39,0:40:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.94,0:40:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.46,0:40:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间 羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.11,0:40:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井…同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.91,0:40:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.78,0:40:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从浪上掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.48,0:40:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.05,0:40:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.32,0:41:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要沉进自己的心里去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.57,0:41:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.54,0:41:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 中断
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.00,0:41:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练中止
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.79,0:41:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过今天的适应性训练
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.88,0:41:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经暂时决定了你们所要驾驶的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.69,0:41:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式的驾驶训练只有真壁一骑和春日井甲洋需要接受
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.06,0:41:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间翔子 远见真矢 要咲良 近藤剑司 小楯卫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们作为候补驾驶员 在训练的同时参加CDC的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.30,0:41:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.71,0:41:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.13,0:41:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.17,0:41:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 你们不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.81,0:42:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事…以后也要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:41:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.13,0:42:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像 有点撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.39,0:42:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也请专注训练 完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.97,0:42:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.15,0:42:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉都傍晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.18,0:42:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在Alvis里对时间都没概念了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.29,0:42:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.40,0:42:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉整个大脑都麻麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.69,0:42:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像大哭过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.44,0:42:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哭…大姐头你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.01,0:42:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我只是打比方啦 打比方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.30,0:42:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.78,0:42:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什么笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.75,0:42:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 一骑同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.11,0:42:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊 可能还在换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.62,0:42:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋也还没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.80,0:42:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…为什么没事啊 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.95,0:43:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是不是不适合啊 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.27,0:43:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你 你为什么想当驾驶员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.44,0:43:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…因为是义务 爸妈也会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.51,0:43:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 还有想在一起的人…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.63,0:43:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在一起的人…是说谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.24,0:43:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也不是特指谁 就是大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.45,0:43:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 实战就不是这么简单的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.86,0:43:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.32,0:43:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.61,0:43:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道以后会碰上什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.56,0:43:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想想就觉得害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.66,0:43:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.62,0:43:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.83,0:43:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然…可能什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.46,0:44:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是起码在危险的时候 我会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.44,0:44:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会说这种话 真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.42,0:44:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.23,0:44:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在身边 我就放心许多了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.63,0:44:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话说 直到刚才我还两腿发抖 路都走不利索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.14,0:44:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.40,0:44:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.34,0:44:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.26,0:44:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.13,0:44:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.14,0:44:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了 春日井也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.63,0:44:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.21,0:44:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.03,0:44:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都在等我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.61,0:44:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说 好歹也是同伴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.27,0:44:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是想我们丢下你们就直说咯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.16,0:45:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.07,0:45:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我爸妈说回去的时候顺道去我家澡堂泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可太好了 我全身都冷透了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.36,0:45:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.67,0:45:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.60,0:45:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯 我们也能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.28,0:45:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说是特别给我们包场
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.74,0:45:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去吧 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…妈妈可能会担心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.60,0:45:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打个电话通知你妈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.37,0:45:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.21,0:45:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.06,0:45:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.39,0:45:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和你们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.18,0:45:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.35,0:45:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这是一切的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.92,0:46:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及不知道将来会如何的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.37,0:46:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后将会一直伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.99,0:46:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.49,0:46:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信总有些东西是永恒的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.57,0:46:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信总有些东西 无论发生什么都不会失落
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.54,0:46:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信即使是在无休无止的战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.89,0:46:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能够找到有价值的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信吧
