Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.63,0:48:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要咲良：新井里美
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.32,0:48:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井甲洋：入野自由
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.51,0:48:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤剑司：白石稔
